&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/assets/img/blog/2019/painting-crowd-with-backs-turned-1200x797.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/img/blog/2019/painting-crowd-with-backs-turned-1200x797.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;alt&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Acrylic on canvas, 760x505mm.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I did this last week. It started off as an experiment with putting circles on a rule-of-thirds grid, then the circles became celestial bodies.&lt;/p&gt;

